# QA Automation Project â€“ SauceDemo

## Overview
This project demonstrates manual and automated testing of the SauceDemo e-commerce application.

## Manual Testing
- Designed 30+ functional test cases (Login, Cart, Checkout)
- Executed all test cases
- Identified and documented 1 business logic defect (checkout allowed with empty cart)

## Automation Testing
Automated core workflows using:
- Selenium WebDriver
- Pytest
- WebDriverWait (Explicit Waits)

### Automated Scenarios:
- Valid Login
- Invalid Login
- Add Item to Cart
- Complete Checkout Flow

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Selenium
- Pytest
- ChromeDriver Manager

